Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H263AA8&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD's Secret Base!\NX Rider Sneaks in!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care. Next?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.70,0:01:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How weird. I'm sure\Nthere was still one left...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,H-he was just here--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He left that behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look after it. You can go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Kawakami, prepare to receive your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir, GOD Supreme Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come for GOD to use\Nyour outstanding surgical skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.70,0:03:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A representative of mine will escort you to\NGOD\N's base in Japan, the Palace of Apollon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Be at Mukougaoka's underground\Ncar park, space C-5, 1400 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It would behoove you to be punctual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD's base in Japan, the Palace of Apollon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling Palace of Apollon. Supreme Commander's\Norders have been relayed to Dr. Kawakami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Destruction of tape confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Palace of Apollon communications room. Deliver\Nremaining doll to electronics engineer Dr. Miyamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger. To Jouhoku College!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs18\i1}Jouhoku College{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You bumped into me too, y'know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This place should do...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What kept you so long? I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Chill out, chill out! I got cake, anpan, and even fruit! Just gimme a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:05:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-Here we go!\N-My stomach's rumbling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this supposed to be!?\NDon't tell me I can eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a dope!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The anpan turned into a doll...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...I've got it! The guy who\Nbumped me in the corridor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry I might die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-The doll...!\N-Creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Orders from GOD's Supreme Commander. Escort\NDr. Miyamoto to the Palace of Apollon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Be at Mukougaoka's underground car park,\Nspace C-5, 1400 hours. Don't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-It disappeared!\N-What's going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So you saw it? Now you must die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Run!\N-Wait!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-No way!\N-Help!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:06:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Help!!\N-Murderer!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-He wants to kill us!\N-Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants to kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-He was so creepy!\N-His face was all grey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All quiet now, not even a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-This weird doll was talking!\N-He said we'd die for hearing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A talking doll? What did it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Something about orders from\NGOD\N's Supreme Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was this doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,On a park bench. There should\Nstill be some pieces there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you take me to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-But...\N-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't worry, I'll be with you. C'mon.\N-Should we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No trace of anything like a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-It really was here!\N-But it... exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'll have to shut those two up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that looks good!\NSome food at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno how you can eat\Nafter a scare like that, Chiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called having priorities.\NLunchtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You must die...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the Death God, Kronos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Perish at my hands!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew GOD were in on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke... I'll kill you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Accursed X Rider! I, Kronos, shall take\Nyour head back to the Palace of Apollon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what is this Palace of Apollon!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this! Kronos Hell Scythe!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life is mine!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kronos! I'll see you at the Palace of Apollon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses! He was at the threshold of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, some coffee should calm you two down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think he wants us dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Keisuke will sort it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But... if he can't, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... No, he won't fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll cross that bridge when we come\Nto it. Don't let it get you down, Mako.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Half past one already...\NKeisuke should be there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two heard a secret order from GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:11:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The place: Mukougaoka's\Nunderground car park, space C-5.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The time: 1400 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible they've changed plans...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Miyamoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Dr. Kawakami.\NIntroduce yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyamoto, from Jouhoku College.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, I'll be escorting you\Nto the Palace of Apollon, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:12:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Its location must remain a\Nsecret even to GOD's allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Put these on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But we--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one of GOD's rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be safer to do as he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been two hours... Just where\Nis this Palace of Apollon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Palace of Apollon's entrance.\NYou may remove your blindfolds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is foggy outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the Palace...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It produces a manmade fog to\Nprevent its being seen from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How thorough...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's GOD for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The surprises are only just beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Palace of Apollon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,At ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,After you, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:14:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This elevator descends ten metres every second.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, we're a\Nhundred metres underground?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a nuclear blast wouldn't reach us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold the Palace of Apollon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Drs. Kawakami and Miyamoto.\NI am GOD's Supreme Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The pleasure's ours, Supreme Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Give them the tour of our Japanese\Nbase, the Palace of Apollon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir. Since the Supreme Commander wills\Nit, follow me and I'll show you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This first room is GOD's\NSecurity Division's gymnasium.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The Security Division is comprised of champion-class\Nmartial artists and athletes from around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Second is GOD's Communication Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD's satellites orbiting Earth let us\Ntransmit to and receive from any location.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Next...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:16:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This third room is Technology, the fourth\Nis Personnel, and fifth is Vehicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sixth is GD, seventh is\NStrategy, and eighth is Medical.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Supreme Commander's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean... GOD's Supreme\NCommander is in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I don't know who's within. Only the Chief of GOD's\NSecret Police, Apollo Geist, has entered this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, doctors? Now that the tour is\Nover, will you work at the Palace of Apollon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected this. It's\Nlike an underground fortress!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have said it better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see something even more interesting\Nif you look through the window behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Miyamoto should find it especially so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I should...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell Dr. Miyamoto who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor of electronics at Jouhoku College, and\NGOD agent, Miyamoto Daigo. Code number 606.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's lying! You've created a\Nduplicate of me! I am Miyamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stop acting, Jin Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you've seen through it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:18:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD Supreme Commander! If you saw through my\Ndisguise, why bring me to the Palace of Apollon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD has bases of this class all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke, what do you think\Nyou can accomplish by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can crush you! Even ants\Nbring down concrete walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well said. GOD needs\Ncourageous people like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give you the highest\Nposition in GOD! Join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I expected more from GOD's Supreme Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you even understand one human's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I really seem like that kind of person!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Then sacrifice yourself\Nto GOD in the Palace of Apollon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The wall's down. Bring it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:19:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD made a mistake letting me go free!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now to check out the Supreme Commander's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is--!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The warriors of Ancient Greece\Nfought to the death in the colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, face the pride of GOD's fighters!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:22:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctors, this is the individual\Non whom I'd like you to operate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:23:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What sort of operation is GOD's Supreme\NCommander overseeing in the Palace of Apollon?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Beware, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.84,0:23:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider has infiltrated the Palace of Apollon,\Nwhere the supposedly dead Apollo Geist awaits.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.80,0:23:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, GOD's monster Kerberos targets\NTachibana Toubei with his Fire Plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A showdown between Apollo Geist and the\NX Rider, and the imminent Fire Plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"Apollo Geist Strikes Back! X Rider, Beware!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.56,0:23:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.56,0:23:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.15,0:23:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.15,0:23:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.07,0:23:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.07,0:23:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.28,0:23:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.28,0:23:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.12,0:23:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.12,0:23:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:24:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:24:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.75,0:24:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.75,0:24:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.84,0:24:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.84,0:24:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.01,0:24:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.01,0:24:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.10,0:24:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.10,0:24:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider